snippet.title: Do No Harm Gameplay Trailer
snippet.description:
#DoNoHarm #indiegame #doctorgame #lovecraft #cthulhumythos 
A Doctor Simulator with a Lovecraftian twist. Use archaic medical procedures to diagnose and treat patients, but beware—nightmarish entities haunt your every step, causing hallucinations, deception, and deadly consequences. Survive 30 days of perilous decisions.

WISHLIST on Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/3138780/Do_No_Harm/
